Subprog INIT_BYLEG(VALEUR)
Variable Char    VALEUR()
  Raz [M]FLGKEY, [M:DIA]REFNUM, [M:DIA]JOT, [M:DIA]POT, [M:DIA]JOT2, [M:DIA]POT2, [M]AVGCPC
